node.text:
Did you know that I’m holding some fun giveaways throughout the month of July in my stories? Come join us today and vote for tomorrow’s giveaway! My favorite sharpener or some fun teacher pens? Which will it be? Come share your opinion!

The winning teacher fave will be tomorrow’s prize!

P.S. These giveaways are super easy to enter. No following, commenting, or anything else required. Just slide an emoji over and you are entered!

They’re just a fun way to celebrate the last month of summer with you!

So go vote now and tune into tomorrow’s stories for the giveaway! ❤️

node.text: Summer is the perfect time to prep for birthdays! 🧁 I always get asked what I put inside these birthday bags. I’m linking a blog post in my bio that includes pictures and links to everything! http://bit.ly/bdayblogpost

Anyone else fall in love with this size bin last year? 🎯 didn’t bring this size back, but I found the exact same size in these fun colors at @michaelsstores this week! I took a picture of the label for you (scroll left) in case you’re searching for them this summer.

Classroom Tip: Don’t toss any worksheets/papers your class didn’t have time to complete. Save them and when you have enough for a day, use them to create sub plans! 

To learn more teacher tips, register for the Classroom Environment + Design Conference using the link in my bio!

You’ll have immediate, lifetime access to the sessions. Tickets are only for sale until July 21, so be sure to grab them now!

PRE-SALE🚨Teachers have been requesting a weekly newsletter template for years now and I finally had time to work on them! I.am.obsessed! 😍

I’ve always been a monthly newsletter type, but these are making me reconsider. 😂

The designs are all done and I’m now working on the Spanish versions. Since so many of you have been waiting for so long, I decided to do a pre-sale discount!

If you purchase right now, you will have access to them as soon as they are complete. They are currently listed OVER 50% off until they are finished and uploaded.

Link in profile if you want to grab them at this price. https://bit.ly/weeklynewsletters
